[[File:2x19_wicket_magic_shoes.jpg|thumb|right|250px|Teebo conjured magic shoes from vines.]]
'''Magic shoes''' were created by the [[Ewok/Legends|Ewok]] [[Teebo/Legends|Teebo]] so that [[Gender/Legends|he]] and his friend [[Wicket Wystri Warrick/Legends|Wicket Wystri Warrick]] could navigate across [[Sinkhole/Legends|sinkholes]] in the [[Vacant Valley]]. The shoes were created from [[Plant/Legends|vines]] that Teebo [[Magic/Legends|conjured]] into coils.<ref name="Bringing Up Norky" />

